{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"descendant-or-self","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/descendant-or-self","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n</p><p>El eje <code>descendant-or-self</code> indica el nodo de contexto y todos sus descendientes. <b>No</b> se incluyen los nodos atributos y namespaces - el <code>parent</code> de un nodo <code>attribute</code> es un nodo elemento, pero los nodos <code>attribute</code> no son los hijos de sus padres.\n</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"El eje descendant-or-self indica el nodo de contexto y todos sus descendientes. No se incluyen los nodos atributos y namespaces - el parent de un nodo attribute es un nodo elemento, pero los nodos attribute no son los hijos de sus padres.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"descendant-or-self","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"descendant-or-self","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"descendant-or-self","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"descendant-or-self","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/xpath/axes/descendant-or-self","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/xpath/axes/descendant-or-self/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Axes","title":"Ejes"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Axes/descendant-or-self","title":"descendant-or-self"}],"pageTitle":"descendant-or-self - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}